      • isSuitableSdk

        @Deprecated
public boolean isSuitableSdk(Sdk sdk)
        Deprecated. 
        Used for automatically assigning an SDK to the project when it gets created. If no SDK is specified in the template project and there is no specific SDK chooser step, the SDK which is set for the project is the highest version SDK for which isSuitableSdk returns true.
        Parameters:
        sdk - the candidate SDK
        Returns:
        true if the SDK can be used for this project type, false otherwise
